Event.info: OSINT - New Matrix Ransomware Variants Installed Via Hacked Remote Desktop Services

Attribute.value: Two new Matrix Ransomware variants were discovered this week by MalwareHunterTeam that are being installed through hacked Remote Desktop services. While both of these variants encrypt your computer's files, one is a bit more advanced with more debugging messages and the use of cipher to wipe free space.
